Simple file server made using flask. It's possible to view files on it.

The frontend was made using https://github.com/Wildog/flask-file-server as base.

The backend was made from scratch.

1.The server uses sessions to keep the user logged in.

2. The server uses cookies the store the selection to see supported files.

3. The server meets the requirement of showing files.

Server link: https://file-server-aloysio-heroku.herokuapp.com/

Therefore this fulfills the requirements of class 12.